The government's decision:

In view of the increasing number of patients in various departments of Padma Bhushan Vasantdada Patil Government Hospital, Sangli under the Department, administrative approval is being granted under this Government Decision for the purchase of equipment and equipment mentioned in the table below in the amount of Rs. 18,50,00, 000 / - (Rupees Eighteen Crore Fifty Lakhs only) (including all taxes) out of the provision available under the State Plan in the interest of the patient for disinfection of surgical equipment, including clothing and dressing of the patients, subject to the following conditions:
Conditions: -
1) This administrative approval 2024-25 is being made in this financial year from the funds sanctioned and available under the State Plan to the institution concerned.
2) The Government issued a "Manual of Procedure for Office Procurement to be carried out by the Government Department" in this regard by the Department of Industries, Power and Labour.
